1
00:00:11,570 --> 00:00:14,860
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="30">Daemons of the Shadow Realm</font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:15,670 --> 00:00:18,780
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>All the pain I've experienced</b></font>

3
00:00:22,290 --> 00:00:27,150
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Has traveled through my veins</b></font>

4
00:00:29,090 --> 00:00:32,290
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And passed through my heart</b></font>

5
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:39,390
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>By the time I've forgotten, it arrives</b></font>

6
00:00:39,390 --> 00:00:40,500
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>In my brain</b></font>

7
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:42,540
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I guess it's not that bad</b></font>

8
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:45,570
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>But there's this tiny little draft</b></font>

9
00:00:45,570 --> 00:00:50,070
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Of resentment and sadness</b></font>

10
00:00:50,070 --> 00:00:53,910
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Just let me have this</b></font>

11
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,500
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm spineless</b></font>

12
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:01,090
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>All my words and tears</b></font>

13
00:01:01,090 --> 00:01:04,790
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And these feathers grown from my feelings</b></font>

14
00:01:04,790 --> 00:01:07,880
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'll put all of them on my back</b></font>

15
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:11,030
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Well, see you later</b></font>

16
00:01:11,030 --> 00:01:14,850
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'll leave it all behind here</b></font>

17
00:01:14,850 --> 00:01:16,120
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm not scared</b></font>

18
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,140
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Up in the sky</b></font>

19
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:21,260
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>See these feathers flutter in the wind</b></font>

20
00:01:21,260 --> 00:01:27,100
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And follow along</b></font>

21
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,750
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="25"><font color="#268465">Zenko-Koro
 Tiger At the Front Door, Wolf At the Back</font></font></b></font>

22
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:15,750
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#af2d1b">Episode 4
<font size="18">Jin and Yuru</font></font></font></b></font>

23
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:18,260
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="35"><b>Danno</b></font></font></font>

24
00:12:28,470 --> 00:12:29,970
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an2}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="35"><font color="#dce9ed">Daemons of the Shadow Realm</font></font></font></b></font>

25
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:09,550
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Keep watching me</b></font>

26
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:14,380
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>So I can't leave</b></font>

27
00:22:19,190 --> 00:22:21,800
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hold me</b></font>

28
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:27,250
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>So I won't start crying</b></font>

29
00:22:30,530 --> 00:22:33,610
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>A tailwind blows</b></font>

30
00:22:33,610 --> 00:22:43,040
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>A thread runs down my spine, and
when it reaches my bloodstream</b></font>

31
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:46,220
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Ah</b></font>

32
00:22:46,220 --> 00:22:56,340
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I've found wings that
might let me fly again</b></font>

33
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:58,960
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Maybe</b></font>

34
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:06,310
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>If you haven't left the nest yet</b></font>

35
00:23:06,310 --> 00:23:12,870
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Then we can fly together</b></font>

36
00:23:26,590 --> 00:23:27,960
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="23"><font color="#a24f43">Next Episode
 Preview</font></font></font></b></font>

